<div class="prompt container">
  <p class="container-content">
    You should run for office! No, really. Has anyone ever told you that? Here's what to do next. Let's find out what offices are opening up in your district.
  </p>
  <button class="reveal-form container-content">Tell Me More</button>
</div>
<div class="form container">
  <p class="form-element container-content">Enter your address and we'll show you which local legislative offices that are coming up for election soon.</p>
  <form class="container-content">
    <div class="form-element container-content">
      <label>Street Address:</label>
      <input class="input"  type="text" name="address[street]">
    </div>
    <div class="form-element container-content">
      <label>City:</label>
      <input class="input"  type="text" name="address[city]">
    </div>
    <div class="form-element container-content">
      <label>State:</label>
      <select class="input"  name="address[state]">
